            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "Anacites are solar-powered constructs, although they can function at reduced capacity away from light. In areas of darkness, they gain the sickened condition.",
                "name": "Sunlight Dependency",
                "ability_type": "Extraordinary",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex"
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "As a move action, an anacite predator drone can lock on to a target within 60 feet that it can see. The anacite can have only one locked target at a time. Against the anacite\u2019s attacks, a locked target gains no benefit from concealment less than total concealment, and a locked target reduces its bonus to AC due to cover by 2.",
